{"lemma":"لَفْظَة","slug":"لَفْظَة","root":"ل.ف.ظ","root_slug":"ل-ف-ظ","root_link":"/words/roots/ل-ف-ظ","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n37878","n37880"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%84%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%92%D8%B8%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"instance noun of لَفَظَ (lafaẓa) an instance of articulating, an utterance, (an exact) word"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun from the verb لَفَظَ (lafaẓa)."},"ipa":["/laf.ðˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n37878","headword_ar":"لَفَظَهُ","root":"lfZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa bihi","text_ar":"لَفَظَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafoZN","text_ar":"لَفْظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, S, M, Msb;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafiZahu","text_ar":"لَفِظَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafiZa bihi","text_ar":"لَفِظَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ibn-"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2667},{"kind":"text","text":"Abbád, K.) but the former is that which is commonly known; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ejected it; cast it forth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disgorged it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (T, S, M, Msb, K;) namely a thing that was in his mouth; (T;) his spittle, &c.; (Msb;) from ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino","text_ar":"مِنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":") his mouth. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa","text_ar":"لَفَظَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone, [elliptically,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ejected what had entered between his teeth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of food. (TA.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZati AlHay~apu sam~ahaA","text_ar":"لَفَظَتِ الحَيَّةُ سَمَّهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The serpent ejected its poison."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa","text_ar":"لَفَظَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSobahu","text_ar":"عَصْبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ejected his spittle that stuck and dried in his mouth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he died;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa nafosahu","text_ar":"لَفَظَ نَفْسَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above; (M, TA;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa","text_ar":"لَفَظَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"alone. (M, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqado lafaZa lijaAmahu","text_ar":"وَقَدْ لَفَظَ لِجَامَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [as to the letter and the meaning like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a waqado dalaqa lijaAmahu","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ وَقَدْ دَلَقَ لِجَامَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came harassed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distressed, by thirst and fatigue."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, M, Z, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZati Alr~aHimu maA='a AlfaHoli","text_ar":"لَفَظَتِ الرَّحِمُ مَا=ءَ الفَحْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The womb ejected the seminal fluid of the stallion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZahu AlbaHoru","text_ar":"لَفَظَهُ البَحْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sea cast it forth upon the shore;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;) namely a fish; (TA;) or a beast. (Msb.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa AlbaHoru bimaA","text_ar":"لَفَظَ البَحْرُ بِمَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiyhi A_ilaY Al$~uTuwTi","text_ar":"فِيهِ اـِلَى الشُّطُوطِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sea cast forth what was within it to the shores."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qaA='ati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"قَا=ءَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ukolahaA walafaZato xabiyoy^ahaA","text_ar":"اُكْلَهَا وَلَفَظَتْ خَبِيْيَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The earth disclosed her vegetables, and revealed her hidden things."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in this art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qyA^","text_ar":"قيا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"لَفَظَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Almay~ita","text_ar":"المَيِّتَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The earth cast forth the dead;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did not receive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"admit, the dead."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZati AlbilaAdu A^aholahaA","text_ar":"لَفَظَتِ البِلَادُ اَهْلَهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The countries cast forth their inhabitants"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa","text_ar":"لَفَظَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlkalaAmi","text_ar":"بِالكَلَامِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biqawolK","text_ar":"بِقَوْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAl$~aYo'i","text_ar":"بِالشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafaZa Alqawola","text_ar":"لَفَظَ القَوْلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafoZN","text_ar":"لَفْظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He uttered, spoke forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bihi","text_ar":"بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tlf~Z","text_ar":"تلفّظ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) It is said in the Kur, [l. 17,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA yalofiZu mino qawolK","text_ar":"مَا يَلْفِظُ مِنْ قَوْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He doth not utter a saying"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: where Kh. reads"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA yalofaZu","text_ar":"ما يَلْفَظُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": both forms of the verb being used in this sense [as is implied in the K.]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n37880","headword_ar":"لَفْظَةٌ","root":"lfZ","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lafoZN","text_ar":"لَفْظٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}